SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."AddedToLib", "t"."AppUserId", "t"."Author", "t"."BookImg", "t"."Description", "t"."ISBN", "t"."NoPage", "t"."Publisher", "t"."PublisherDate", "t"."Title", "t"."ViewBook", "r"."Id", "r"."AppUserId", "r"."BookId", "r"."Comment", "r"."DateCreated", "r"."Rating", "r"."Title"
FROM (
    SELECT "b"."Id", "b"."AddedToLib", "b"."AppUserId", "b"."Author", "b"."BookImg", "b"."Description", "b"."ISBN", "b"."NoPage", "b"."Publisher", "b"."PublisherDate", "b"."Title", "b"."ViewBook"
    FROM "Books" AS "b"
    WHERE "b"."Id" = @__Id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS "t"
